{"tid":2077044,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"擁英藉林鄭月娥又爆大鑊：面對現實，香港人","createTime":"2020-06-24T04:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:00:45.000Z","uid":219635,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eedb5e7ccf3e0af0d44a53ae62af604528ae2d9c","tid":2077044,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T04:01:22.000Z","msg":"「蘋果日報」<br />\n特首林鄭月娥星期二（23日）晚，喺中國發展高層論壇網絡簡報會致辭，話自從全國人大決定訂立「港版國安法」之後，有大量來自外國政府嘅不公允批評。佢總結呢啲批評係「雙重標準」和「偽善」，話所有指控中國嘅國家，本身都有國家安全法。<br />\n<br />\n老公同囝囝都係英籍嘅林鄭仲話，聽到好多外國人講，要畀香港人擁有外國居民資格，或者威脅要制裁香港，聲稱同香港人「站在一起」。<span style=\"color: red;\">但林鄭形容，呢啲外國人講嘅都係「花言巧語」、「偽善」，話要放長雙眼，睇吓當佢哋國民嘅反應或政治環境，令呢啲「撐港人」行動變得不受歡迎嗰陣，會變成點樣嘅結果喎。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/5MBCHQ5UPIJV7EU5K7545TFPYA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F5MBCHQ5UPIJV7EU5K7545TFPYA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=71cc07c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F5MBCHQ5UPIJV7EU5K7545TFPYA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=2d40a028\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/5MBCHQ5UPIJV7EU5K7545TFPYA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n連林鄭條仆街都知英國佬又撚香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你香港人冇錢，我收留你把撚呀，三十年後未死晒，英國佬可能考慮會出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人都係自己救自己好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟流浮山2百刀手落元朗快啲，還是英國佬出真手快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c866293ecaaa8eb39cc7f0572cd4976d528d54a","tid":2077044,"uid":13724,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"eedb5e7ccf3e0af0d44a53ae62af604528ae2d9c","tid":2077044,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T04:01:22.000Z","msg":"「蘋果日報」<br />\n特首林鄭月娥星期二（23日）晚，喺中國發展高層論壇網絡簡報會致辭，話自從全國人大決定訂立「港版國安法」之後，有大量來自外國政府嘅不公允批評。佢總結呢啲批評係「雙重標準」和「偽善」，話所有指控中國嘅國家，本身都有國家安全法。<br />\n<br />\n老公同囝囝都係英籍嘅林鄭仲話，聽到好多外國人講，要畀香港人擁有外國居民資格，或者威脅要制裁香港，聲稱同香港人「站在一起」。<span style=\"color: red;\">但林鄭形容，呢啲外國人講嘅都係「花言巧語」、「偽善」，話要放長雙眼，睇吓當佢哋國民嘅反應或政治環境，令呢啲「撐港人」行動變得不受歡迎嗰陣，會變成點樣嘅結果喎。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/5MBCHQ5UPIJV7EU5K7545TFPYA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F5MBCHQ5UPIJV7EU5K7545TFPYA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=71cc07c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F5MBCHQ5UPIJV7EU5K7545TFPYA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=2d40a028\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/5MBCHQ5UPIJV7EU5K7545TFPYA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n連林鄭條仆街都知英國佬又撚香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你香港人冇錢，我收留你把撚呀，三十年後未死晒，英國佬可能考慮會出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人都係自己救自己好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟流浮山2百刀手落元朗快啲，還是英國佬出真手快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci